  allLines:
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You know there are a lot of jokes I could\u2019ve made with the word
      \u201Cpump\u201D but I kinda forgot about all of them when we made eye contact.
      Fuck, that was kinda cringe wasn\u2019t it?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 7956698841550424776, guid: 2dfa7703027856e42aa0ad06571044c3, type: 3}
    sentence: "Pfft- I can\u2019t believe that made me blush. Also, don\u2019t worry
      I thought of at least 5 disgusting jokes as soon as the words left my own mouth."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: -5402865554541780227, guid: b446a76fbc2023446ad757d3ac4b927e, type: 3}
    sentence: "And I thought of at least 5 more myself in the span of 3 seconds.
      You know if we didn\u2019t have a third listening in right now, I\u2019d have
      you doubling over laughing."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: -1160322238068995058, guid: e79cf994b0112f542bb5904bcd06966b, type: 3}
    sentence: "Oh I\u2019m sure there are other ways you\u2019d have me doubling
      ove-"
    eventTrigger: 
